Package universitysystem.entity

Class Dean

java.lang.Object
universitysystem.entity.User
universitysystem.entity.Employee
universitysystem.entity.Dean
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<User>, CanCreate, CanLogin, Runnable, Subscription
public class Dean extends Employee implements Serializable
The Dean class presents a dean within the university system, extending the functionality of the Employee class. A dean is responsible for managing employee requests, handling complaints, and overseeing a specific faculty.
